 }}
/>


  <!-- HighlightedPosts Widget ******* -->

  <BlogLatestPosts
    title="Find out more content in our Blog"
    information={`Dive into our blog to discover expert advice on web development, app design, e-commerce strategies, SEO best practices, and more. Whether you're a seasoned entrepreneur or just starting your digital journey, our informative articles and engaging content are tailored to help you stay ahead of the curve and succeed in the ever-evolving landscape of digital marketing. 
                `}
  />

  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Discover answers to commonly asked questions about Brandify Media's services, processes, and expertise."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'What services does Brandify Media offer??',
        description:
          "Brandify Media offers a comprehensive range of digital solutions including web development, app development, e-commerce solutions, SEO services, hosting, payment gateway integration, and themes/templates.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How long does it take to develop a website or app?',
        description:
          'The timeline for website or app development varies depending on the complexity of the project, features required, and client specifications. We work closely with clients to establish realistic timelines and strive to deliver projects within agreed-upon deadlines.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I see examples of your previous work?',
        description:
          "Absolutely! We have a portfolio showcasing our previous projects across various industries. Feel free to explore our portfolio to see examples of our web development, app development, e-commerce solutions, and more. Additionally, we can provide case studies and client testimonials upon request for a more in-depth understanding of our capabilities and expertise.",
